text: Maika Monroe (born Dillon Monroe Buckley; born May 29, 1993) is an American actress. She was born in Santa Barbara, California. Her first well known role was in It Follows (2014). Monroe later appeared in The Guest (2014), Tau (2018), Greta (2018) and Watcher (2022), and the horror movies Significant Other (2022) and Longlegs (2024). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Santa Barbara, California
